^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Very interesting hand. First let's talk about the bidding. We will get to the play after. Very hard hand to play. As to the bidding. The first two bids are standard. There are some implications about my bid. I am basically showing the same 3S bid I would have had if lisa had passed--4 card support and less than a limit raise. If I had a limit raise, I would have bid 3H as that is a "cue bid" of lisa's known suit. Granted, I have a really bad 3S bid, but I figured jana was short in hearts since I had so many. |
