NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|So double (which is stolen bid, saying I intended to bid 2S, or even pass are also acceptable. I think darlene should bid 4H rather than 4D. she knows they have a 9 card fit. If lisa happens to have diamonds, they might even be making 6 due to the double fit.|
